      "para_id": "Q001758.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Lamma , his lady , Bau-ninam , chief butler of Ur-Ninĝirsu , the beloved en priest of Nanše , fashioned her women's wig for the well-being of Šulgi , the powerful man , king of Urim ."
